summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Volume 26, page 33 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 12034 and 12038 15th Avenue NE from Single Family 7200 (SF 7200) to Lowrise 3 (L3) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Julie Pattison, Stacy Pattison-Daniels & Winiver Thompson, C.F. 301537 Appl. 9505505)
